text: Kingsborough Community College is a community college in Brooklyn, New York. It is part of the City University of New York's university system. It is located in Manhattan Beach. It was built in 1963. It has around 38,000 students. It has a private beach which is open during the summer. ==References== ==Other websites== *Kingsborough Community College website Category:Colleges and universities in New York City Category:Brooklyn Category:1963 establishments in New York (state)
